text: Anqasqucha (Quechua anqas blue, qucha lake, "blue lake", hispanicized spellings Ancasccocha, Ancascocha, Anccasccocha, Angascocha, Angasjocha, also Anqasqocha) may refer to: * Anqasqucha (Acobambilla), a mountain in the Acobambilla District, Huancavelica Province, Huancavelica Region, Peru * Anqasqucha (Ayacucho), a lake in the Ayacucho Region, Peru * Anqasqucha (Huancavelica), a lake in the Acobambilla District, Huancavelica Province, Huancavelica Region, Peru
title: Anqasqucha
